Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:09.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:20.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:39.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:46.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:54.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:00:59.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:07.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:14.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:21.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:28.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:44.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:51.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:54.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that's Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:01:55.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:57.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:58.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where's Onasia?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:00.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's become of Onasia, Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:03.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,And why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:05.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think I know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,You decided this is where\Nyou want to be, right, Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun has made her choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's chosen her own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:27.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:31.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. Yun's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:40.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:44.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I should've come here before\Nwith all my friends from Rubor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:50.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go in together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:53.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:58.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, you've been\Nthrough a lot, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think we all have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:06.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, you don't have\Nany regrets, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:12.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I did want to pray to\Nthe skies in an ancient Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:15.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean I wanted to operate one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:21.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to sit in the captain's\Nchair on the Arcus Prima, just once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:29.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:36.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as if I don't know\Nanything about any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:39.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:44.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,We don't really know\Nanything about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:50.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we must all fall if\Nwe ever want to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,We must fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Uttering screams along the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even as we're racked by fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,With our hearts in our mouths...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:04.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,We must hold on to ourselves and\Nkeep falling and falling endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,And as you continue to fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:09.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,You reach out and cling to something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...because you're so afraid,\Nand you try to hang on somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:17.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we have to let go\Neventually, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:22.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Somewhere at the bottom of that\Nabyss, I promise you I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,The priestesses of Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:12.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually, I suppose we shouldn't\Nbe calling them that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:15.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,But yes, they should be returning soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to finding out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:21.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what decision each of the\Npriestesses of Chor Tempest has made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm looking forward to that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,And what about those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:30.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think they're going to be\Nour last responsibility here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:31.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,At the Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun was supporting us, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:55.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,It almost felt like being in a cradle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of our emotions,\Nall at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:12.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:05.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:26.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:34.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:35.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:39.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me why my heart hurts so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know the answer, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:42.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:44.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why is it that my heart\Nis hurting so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:51.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:09:00.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's what love is, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:07.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:33.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria... She was a\Nstrong person, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was a strong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Secretly meeting with\Na highland priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and before Tempus Spatium too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,That can't be the\Naction of a sane person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:06.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...this will be my last task for\Nthe Chor Tempest Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:11.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope that Tempus\NSpatium will be forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:17.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't forget what Sibylla\NNeviril said during the hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:25.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am not looking to blame\Nanyone for this war we're waging.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how tragic and\Npainful our lives may be now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I believe that it was\Nall meant to happen this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:33.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether or not that is the\Nwill of Tempus Spatium...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:36.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it makes no difference to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:41.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I no longer even care whether\Nit's God's will anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, I do have one\Nquestion for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Despite all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:49.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,...can I still call\Nmyself a Simoun sibylla?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:10:59.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:08.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling you never\Nstopped being a sibylla, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:16.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:20.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:25.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're all waiting on\Nthe observation deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:33.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,You guys can join us later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you do that, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:44.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later too, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Will you dance with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:54.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,The soldiers are watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does it bother you, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:25.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:31.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are still two priestesses\Nwho have not yet entered the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:35.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sibylla Neviril and Sibylla Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:41.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,When do they plan to\Nmake their pilgrimage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,How was the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone seemed really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:57.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, so many smiling faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Were you bored, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:05.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I did some maju by\Nmyself and then had some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,You guys haven't really\Nchanged much. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:11.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose to become a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose to become a woman too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:14.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:16.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Male?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:17.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose to become male also.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:21.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:30.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'll go as soon as\Nthey feel ready to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:32.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,We cannot wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:36.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the most crucial\Ncondition in our peace treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:43.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's not as if a time limit has\Nbeen set for that condition to be met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:49.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,We cannot wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,The reason I didn't choose Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:14:00.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,...wasn't because I didn't\Nwant to betray you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:04.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was simply an excuse to\Nprotect myself from getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wanting to be a good\Ngirl all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:28.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,How childish is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:33.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was sure that both Amuria and\NAer had chosen me as their pair...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,...just as a tool...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:39.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to complete the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:46.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was the one who was drawn\Nto their single-mindedness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:51.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I came to realize that they're\Nboth far more pure in spirit than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:57.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neither of them are\Nafraid of getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:00.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:05.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind to be true\Nto what I'm feeling right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Once you stop trying to subject\Nothers to your own feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:13.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you start to feel as if you can\Nplant your feet on a bigger stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to wait and be\Nconsumed by the waiting anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:22.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to stop blaming\Neverything on the one I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:26.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I want to learn what\Nit's like to be truly loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta! Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:32.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:37.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose to stay female.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:42.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,We will arrange for them to be\Nescorted to the Spring by nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our soldiers will accompany them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose to become a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me too. I chose to become a woman too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:22.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:32.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:38.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:46.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, please wait here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, you morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:57.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:01.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:05.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,No! They can't make Neviril\Nand Aer go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two are our...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:11.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. They're carrying\Nour present on their shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:15.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, is this really part of the\Npeace treaty that Simulacrum agreed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, can they really do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:21.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril and Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:24.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will only go to that\NSpring over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,The eternal present...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:31.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:35.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:38.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:45.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to see you, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:49.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to touch you, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:22.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:23.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:27.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Alty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:38.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:20:00.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,That title is no longer\Nappropriate for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:01.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:05.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have asked permission\Nto give our sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a final farewell before\Nthey go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:13.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the most the Arcus Prima's\Ncaptain could manage to do for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:49.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:57.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,How uncharacteristically\Nbarbaric of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:58.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:01.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:05.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:12.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:14.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer! Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:30.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe, Alty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:34.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:35.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I said don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:37.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:44.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose this is\Ngoodbye, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:46.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:49.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know you two can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:52.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura, Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:21:57.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:02.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:06.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I promise you, someday,\Nwe'll meet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:13.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:16.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell, eternal priestesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.26,0:22:47.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:52.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:59.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:06.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:19.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to get closer to you.\NI want to feel your pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:24.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:28.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:32.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.98,0:23:38.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:44.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.39,0:23:47.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:53.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.50,0:23:59.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:06.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:07.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.81,0:24:11.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the tale of the\Nsibyllae's "tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.15,0:24:16.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on the final\Nepisode of Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.52,0:24:19.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their Portraits\NTheir Portraits.
